Monitored function list:
Minimum requirements (with stat -> __xstat, lstat -> __xlstat)
pread
fflush
fputs_unlocked
fwrite_unlocked

Functional:
Monitored executable can work as usual.
Provide basic list for function call parameters and return values.
Provide comprehensive list for function call parameters and return values.
Output can be configured using MONITOR_OUTPUT environmental variable.
Use Makefile to manage the building process.

Make rules:
all (Compiled filename: fsmon.so)
clean

Language:
C++17 (g++7 or newer required)

Environment:
Ubuntu 16.04.6 LTS